# DataTable Component

The `DataTable` component provides a feature-rich, interactive table for displaying and managing transaction data. It includes functionality for sorting, filtering, pagination, and row selection. The component is designed to handle large datasets efficiently while providing a comprehensive set of tools for data exploration and manipulation.

